 * LilyGo T-LoRa C6 (T3-C6) â€” ESP32-C6-MINI-1U, 4MB flash
 *
 * Hardware:
 *   MCU:     ESP32-C6 (RISC-V single-core, BLE 5.0, Wi-Fi 6, 802.15.4)
 *   Flash:   4 MB
 *   Radio:   SX1262 LoRa on SPI2
 *   LED:     GPIO7 (active HIGH)
 *   Console: USB-Serial/JTAG (built-in)
